                            <p>We may use the Information to contact you or the Child User from time to time, to provide you
                                with the Application, Website or Services, or with important information, required notices
                                and marketing promotions. We will ask you when we need more Information that personally
                                identifies you or the Child User or allows us to contact you or the Child User.</p>
                            <p>In order to make the best use of our Application/Website/Services/ and enable your
                                Information or Information belonging to a Child User to be captured accurately on the
                                Application/Website/Services, it is essential that you or the Child User log-in using your
                                own credentials. You agree and acknowledge that the use of our Application/Website/Services
